Ikka-tt-inn '''Yuba Wis Sin''' neɣ '''Yuba 2''' (s [[Tutlayt Talatint|tlatint]]: IVBA; s [[Tutlayt Tagrikt|tgrikt taqburt]]: Ἰóβας, Ἰóβα nɣ Ἰούβας<ref name="Roller">Roller, Duane W. (2003) ''The World of Juba II and Kleopatra Selene'' "Routledge (UK)". pp. 1–3. {{ISBN|0-415-30596-9}}.</ref>; Iddr gr 48 dat tlalit n Ɛisa - 23 ḍaṛt talalit n Ɛisa) iga agllid n tglditin timaziɣin tiqburin [[Muriṭanya|Mawritanya]] d [[Numidya|Numidya]] ḍart n baba-s u numidya [[Yuba Amzwaru|Yuba amzwaru]]. Ɣ tsga n unbaḍ-nns bahra imursn, ikka-tt-inn iga yan umassan d umara bahra ittuḥtaramn ɣ uzmz-nns. Tamɣrat-nns tamzwarut tga-tt [[Klyupatra Silini Tiss Snat|Klyupatra Silini Tiss Snat]], illi-s n tgllidt [[Miṣra|tamiẓṛit]] [[Klyupatra Tiss Sat|Klyupatra Tiss Sat]] n [[Miẓra Tapṭulmt|Miẓra Tapṭulmt]].
== Tudrt ==
=== Timẓi d tɣri-nns ===
Iga Yuba wiss sin agldun [[Imaziɣen|Amaziɣ]] zɣ [[Numidya]]. Ig waḥdu-t arraw n ugllid [[Yuba Amzwaru|Yuba Amzwaru]]; tamagit n inna-s ur tettyussan. Ɣ usggʷas wis 46 DƐ, innra [[Yulyus Kaysar]] baba-s (ɣ [[Imiɣ n Tapsus|Tapsus]]), tdwl ilmma [[Numidya]] ddaw unbaḍ aṛuman arusrid ɣ 40 DƐ<ref name="Roller" />. Baba-s ikka-tt-inn iga tuṛfa d ujiniṛal [[Pompey]].

Mnnaw n imẓlayn itrarn ar ttinin mas rad ig uwtay-nns lliɣ innra Kaysar ɣ 46 DƐ kra n kkuẓ nɣ sḍis n isggʷasn, hiya rad ilul gr 52 d 50 DƐ. Ɣ tsga yaḍn, anmzray "Duane Roller", ur iflis s maya. Roller yanni is ilul ɣ usggʷas n 48 DƐ acku irm lli ittusmrasn ɣ wawal fllas ɣ [[Tutlayt Tagrikt|tgrikt taqburt]] ''brefos'' isnamk taslmya. Irm i wazzan gr 4 d 6 n isggʷasn iga-t ''pias'' lli ur ssmrisn i Yuba ɣ isugam iqburn. F maya, Roller ar isrus awtay n Yuba 2 lliɣ ixsr baba-s gr sin yyirn d 2 isggʷasn, aylli aɣ-yakkan asakud n tlalit gr 48 d 46 DƐ<ref name=Roller59>Roller, Duane W. (2003) ''The World of Juba II and Kleopatra Selene'' "Routledge (UK)". p. 59. {{ISBN|0-415-30596-9}}.</ref>.

Yiwi [[Yulyus Kaysar]] Yuba wiss sin s Ṛuma. Ɣinn a ɣ ilmd [[Tutlayt talatint|tutlayt talatint]] d [[Tutlayt Tagrikt|tgrikt taqburt]], ittṛuwmn, tettyufka-as tɣlnawt taṛumant<ref name="Roller" />. S tuggʷas mqqurnin lli iskar ɣ tɣri-nns, nnan fll-as mas iga yan sɣ inmuran akkʷ iɣran ɣ Ṛuma ɣ uzmz-ann. Lliɣ ilkm 20 n usggʷas yara adlis-nns amzwaru s uzwl "Roman Archaeology"<ref name="Roller" />. Issnkr-t-id [[Yulyus Kaysar]], ilmma ayyaw-nns Uktawyan (Lli rad ig amnkad [[Awgustus]]). Lliɣ ittimɣur, Imun Yuba 2 d Uktawyan ɣ mnnaw imciṛṛiyn, ilmd zgi-snt kigan f manmk rad ig anssixf. Immaɣ ɣ tasga n Uktawyan ɣ [[imiɣ n Aktum|Imiɣ n Aktyum]].
=== Uɣul-nns s unbaḍ n Numidya ===
Ɣ 30 DƐ, irar-t Uktawyan am ugllid n [[Numidya]]<ref name="MelaRomer1998">{{cite book|author1=Pomponius Mela|author2=Frank E. Romer|title=Pomponius Mela's Description of the World|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6AplSod8IDcC&pg=PA43|year=1998|publisher=University of Michigan Press|isbn=0-472-08452-6|page=43}}</ref><ref name="Gagarin2010">{{cite book|author=Michael Gagarin|title=The Oxford Encyclopedia of Ancient Greece and Rome|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lNV6-HsUppsC&pg=RA4-PA80|year=2010|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-517072-6|page=80}}</ref>. Tg ilmma [[Numidya]] Tuṛfa n Ṛuma. Ḥaqqan aya iga tayafut n twisi-nns i [[Awgustus]] ɣ imzizzl-nns ɣ Hispanya. Isastwa-as itihal-nns d Klyupatra Silini ger 26 DƐ d 20 DƐ, ifk-as yat trzzift, iskr gi-s tagllidt<ref>Roller, Duane W. (2003) The World of Juba II and Kleopatra Selene Routledge (UK){{ISBN|0-415-30596-9}} p. 74</ref>. Ɣ 25 DƐ, tsskcm Ṛuma [[Numidya|Numidya]] (Amr [[Numidya|Numidya]] Tutrimt) ddaw n unbaḍ-nns usrid, yamẓ ilmma Yuba 2 [[Muriṭanya|Mawritanya]] am tgldit-nns<ref name="MelaRomer1998" />.
=== Anbaḍ ɣ Mawritanya ===
Zzɣ aylli aɣ-ittals Strabu, tnbḍ Ṛuma tagldit-nns s tmamkt tusridt (gr 33 DƐ - 25 DƐ) ḍaṛt n tmttant n ugllid amawritan Bukkus Wiss Sin lli tt-inn-ikkan iga tuṛfa n Iṛumiyn, ilmma ifk-tt [[Awgustus]] i [[Yuba II|Yuba 2]] ɣ 25 DƐ<ref>''Geography'' n Strabu ([https://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.01.0239%3Abook%3D17%3Achapter%3D3#note-link15 Strab. 17.3])</ref>. Lliɣ immuti Yuba 2 d Klyupatra Silini s Mawritanya, smman tamaẓunt-nnsn tamaynut ''Kaysarya'' ([[Crcel]] tatrart) f wudm n Awgustus. Tuṣkawin ɣ Kaysaria d Wlili (Volubilis) da mmalnt yan usrks gr tmsdagt Tamiẓrit, Tagrikt d Tṛumiyt.

Ittyunna mas tt-inn-tkka Klyupatra teṭṭaf afus f tsrtit n Yuba II. Yuba II issbɣs, isnal i tẓuṛi, asiggl amassan d usiggl g umzruy agaman. Yuba isnal ula i tsbbabt tawmuritant. Tkka-tt-inn tgldit n Mawritanya tla atig amqqran i tmnkda taṛumiyt. Tkcm tkka-tt-inn tsala tasbbabt d kraygat mani ɣ yilel agraklan, slawan akkʷ d [[Sbanya]] ula [[Ṭṭalyan]]. 
